message:
Had a long satisfying conversation with Uncle, he has resumed walks and physiotherapy is going on regularly. He is even trying acupressure therapy in the Clinic for pain relief... hoping it works substantially !

His son is here and giving company even if he's busy.
He wished me good luck and gave blessings to my daughter for the upcoming future.
Going to Bangalore.... Will be back on Monday night

Good morning 
Rec'd a msg from shah food since being id today they won't be delivering food ,so called Beautie and asked her if food needs to be ordered,she said she would be preparing it.

Visit 1
Jun 6
Time 11:7 am -2:43pm
Purpose of visit well being of prantes 

Today I met aunty and uncle. Both of them were feeling fine. Aunty was at home, and uncle had gone t o Mall Road like he does every day. He also had some work at the bank, so he went there. While uncle was out, aunty and I did some exercise.

After exercising, aunty had to prepare lunch because her maid won‚Äôt be coming for two days ‚Äî she‚Äôs not feeling well. So aunty had to cook lunch herself. I helped her for a while, and then uncle came back. I spoke to uncle, and he said he got late today because he couldn‚Äôt find a taxi.

Aunty mentioned that her maid might go back to her village, but it‚Äôs not confirmed yet.

Just spoke to aunty. Aunty had taken breakfast. Aunty told me that when she goes to see the doctor she will get an X-ray done the same day, she is a little relieved with the medicines. Aunty is not getting physiotherapy done now because  therapist is charging a lot.
